{"tid":846514,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【發展商跪低】加息後即減價 逸瑆12伙勁減近「1球」放售","createTime":"2018-10-03T12:54:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-07T14:10:02.000Z","uid":83582,"like":32,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":74,"replies":[{"pid":"9e7743603d02fcff6fbcf270556472b3cca17aee","tid":846514,"uid":83582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T12:54:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n2018年10月03日 <br />\n<br />\n【發展商跪低】加息後即減價 逸瑆12伙勁減近「1球」放售 <br />\n<br />\n加息後首個新盤劈價賣樓！麗新（488）與市建局發展項目筲箕灣逸瑆銷情慘淡，自上月開售至今，僅賣出5伙單位，發展商見成績差強人意，便修改2號價單將部分單位大幅劈價出售，涉及12伙，減幅普遍達一成，如12樓A室，實用面積386方呎，原定價971.6萬元，大減至874.4萬元，減價97.2萬元或一成，最新呎價22,653元。另發展商新增「540天升級靈活付款計劃」吸引買家入市，可獲4%折扣優惠。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20181003/58753098\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181003%2F58753098&d=W5%2B94bhWvdJEOBwLKzKFJP755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=12efbf1f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181003%2F58753098&h=ded77e79\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20181003/58753098</a>"},{"pid":"58308bfa3a7af314830a690e442c69d5f56ec71c","tid":846514,"uid":75877,"like":127,"dislike":0,"score":127,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T12:56:36.000Z","msg":"已賣出5伙單位業主: 屌你老母"},{"pid":"0d8a4ff72d477584564466fffed306aa2626d807","tid":846514,"uid":42921,"like":46,"dislike":1,"score":45,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T13:00:40.000Z","msg":"加息唔加價，而家啲發展商咁蠢"},{"pid":"c90eed650cd15d1d543aabf572a1b43ae9d4100f","tid":846514,"uid":40397,"like":29,"dislike":1,"score":28,"quote":{"pid":"58308bfa3a7af314830a690e442c69d5f56ec71c","tid":846514,"uid":75877,"like":127,"dislike":0,"score":127,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T12:56:36.000Z","msg":"已賣出5伙單位業主: 屌你老母"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T13:02:31.000Z